Function to check the variable null or NA

Source: R/help_model_functions.R
check_null_na.Rd

Function to check the variable null or NA

check_null_na(variable)

Arguments

variable

name of variable or list of variable to check

Value

-1 or -2 as error, else return 0 as success

Examples

var = c("a")
check_null_na(var)

#> [1] 0
